messages.messageBody:
Has anyone heard of the Stratford Career Institute? It is an online
college level school based in Canada. I've researched this school.
It seems to have a good reputation and is accredited. However, I
can't find anyone who has tried it and I don't know much about how an
online school works except that this one is inexpensive and you work
at your own pace. Such a school would be perfect for me and my wife
because of work and home schooling duties.

Anyone who has some information, or wants to know more about this
school, please email me at backtocebu at yahoo.

Jim
